#    - copy the dir /amy/runs/aananiky/tc/licensing to the training
#    - cd training
#    - remove all files with the extensions txt and log
#    - remove all files with the name started with "perf" and "Lesson"
#    - make all files executable
#    - remove all content
#    - create a new file named "hello.txt" with the content "Hello World !"
#    - copy all from /net/amy-dev1/scratch/performance/reg/tot_master/netlisting/HEN_based_netlisting_full_chip/baseline
#    - rename all *.transcript files to the corresponding *.log
#    - print the first 20 lines of each file
#    - print the last 20 lines of each file
##########################################################################################################################

